Instance Method

assignOwnership(source:type:contains:about:origin:)

Assign ownership to a given source.

Declaration

func assignOwnership(source: String, type: TikiSdkDataTypeEnum, contains: Array<String>, about: String? = nil, origin: String? = nil) async throws -> String

Return Value

A base64 url-safe no-padding representation of the ownership transaction id.

Parameters

source

The identification of the data source.

type

The type of data source (point, pool or stream) identified by TikiSdkDataTypeEnum.

contains

The list of items the data contains.

about

A description about the data.

origin

Optional override for default origin.

Note
